            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Choosing a preschool for your little one is a significant decision, and I couldn't be happier with the experience we've had at Little Millennium Bavdhan. They involve parents along with children in each and every event so that the bonding becomes stronger.\nThe curriculum at the school is thoughtfully designed to encourage curiosity, creativity, and social development. Through engaging activities and play-based learning, my child has blossomed both academically and emotionally. I've been consistently impressed by the variety of educational materials and resources available to support my child's individual learning journey.\nThey take limited children in one batch so that they can focus on each child and personal attention was given. They let the parent know about the behavioral issues in the child as well, as each teacher gets training from the child psychologist. I love this concept personally.\nAbove all, the genuine care and affection the teachers show towards the children is heartwarming. They create a safe and loving environment where every child feels valued and encouraged to explore the world around them.\nI wholeheartedly recommend this school to any parent seeking a nurturing, enriching, and joyful start to their child's educational journey, where my child never wanted to miss the school for a single day. Believe me, this school is not like other schools. As a cautious parent I am so much relieved.",
